data.description: Home for Auction, Don't miss your opportunity to own this 3-bedroom  2-bath home for a great price. Bring your highest and best offers!! Come out for a certified pre-inspected home auction on 2/10 From 11 am -1 pm  The bones are great, and only need your creative touch to reimagine this home! This house has the ideal floor plan with major potential. ***Remind your buyers this property may qualify for a renovation loan***.
